name: Jump!
description: Hop up to the sloper and mantle.

name: Whelmed
description: Start with a left hand high on a decent sidepull and right hand on a crimp.

name: Bubbles No-Hands
description: Climb the boulder with no hands!

name: No Pitons Here No-Hands
description: Climb the boulder with no hands!

name: Flying Goat Boy
description: Hop up to the sloper and mantle.

name: Schist Lip
description: Start sitting, rock over at the tree and continue diagonaling up or drop off.

name: Squatter Variation
description: Start with a high right hand on the arête and hop a foot up to the pimple.

name: Red Traverse
description: Traverse right, staying below the lip.

name: Fin Traverse
description: Start on the right side of the fin, shuffle to the left and then pull up to the main boulder, exiting near the top of The Pit.

name: Lowe Rider Stand
description: Traverse the detached flake, starting from a good left foot.

name: Joel’s Slab
description: Optional if you're up for it!

name: Footless Traverse
description: An option hard and grand ending. Climb in 1 or 2 parts!
